title: Fire (disambiguation)
content:
Fire may refer to:

  • Fire, the result of using logs with a tinderbox.
  • Firemaking, the skill used to light said fires.

Monsters[edit | edit source]

  • Entrana firebird
  • Fire elemental
  • Fire giant
  • Fire Warrior of Lesarkus
  • Fire wizard

Items[edit | edit source]

  • Elemental staves:
    • Staff of fire
    • Fire battlestaff
    • Mystic fire staff
  • Gnomish firelighters:
    • Blue firelighter
    • Green firelighter
    • Purple firelighter
    • Red firelighter
    • White firelighter
  • Potions:
    • Antifire potion
    • Antifire mix
    • Extended antifire
    • Extended antifire mix
  • Anti-dragon shield
  • Blank fire rune, used in The Slug Menace quest.
  • Dragonfire shield
  • Fire arrows, used in the Underground Pass quest.
  • Fire cape, the reward for completing the TzHaar Fight Cave.
  • Fire max cape
  • Fire max hood
  • Fire feather, used in the Heroes' Quest.
  • Fire giant bone, and its polished version, used in the Rag and Bone Man II quest.
  • Fire orb
  • Fire rune
  • Fire rune pack
  • Earth rune, used in The Slug Menace quest.
  • Fire talisman
  • Fire tiara
  • Tome of fire

  • Construction objects:

  • Fire spells:

  • Music tracks:

    • Fire and Brimstone

  • Chasm of Fire, a location.
  • Dragonfire
  • Fire Altar, a Runic altar.
  • Charge Fire Orb, a spell.
  • Obelisk of Fire, an elemental obelisk.
